</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>> and yes it is a roleplaying game, the designers INTENDED the

<BR>&gt; game to be that way. but look, if you wanna group yoru paladin
<BR>&gt; with a shadow knight, go ahead.. who am i to tell you how to
<BR>&gt; play?
<P>exactly thats what I am saying. I would hate to see people attack me and my friend just because we are grouped and thats not supposed to be "in their idea of roleplaying" everquest environment
<P>just do ruin someone elses fun. and attacking someone else
<BR>&gt; randomly and completly out of character is absurd not the other
<BR>&gt; way around.
<P>What makes you think I'll do this? I am just fighing to make sure that no more limitations are placed upon our pvp server and that people should not be forced to roleplay in some special fashion, eg to do racial wars and such.. it will come naturally
<P>If i see everyone around me acting like taht and its fun ill do it too, but its is plain killing ill do that too as well so ill just adapt.
<BR>
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
